Ramirez  said state oil company Petroleos de Venezuela SA will
invest more than $4 billion in a plan to convert heavy crudes
into lighter ones at its Puerto La Cruz refinery, Agencia
Venezolana de Noticias reported.  The refineryâ€™s upgrader will convert heavy and extra heavy
crudes from the Orinoco Belt into lighter products including
